Author: Pali
Title: 📌⚡[AIRDROP][ANN][ICO][PRESALE] 🌐🔴 ISH - International science hub 🚀 🔴 🌐
Body: Quote from: khanhnv6 on August 12, 2018, 03:46:59 PM I like the project, plan, route clearly. http://bit.ly/2KO14lQ   Thank you!  Here's an update from our CEO:   Quote from: Denis Zyryanov We start the project as a social network for scientists and IT specialists, so that they have a comfortable environment for communication and work, where they can gather in teams, come up with and discuss new ideas, replenish their portfolio and share it with people.  After we gather a large number of users within the platform, we will launch the functionality in the form of tender and crowdfunding systems, as well as provide a knowledge base and a wallet for crypto-transactions . As soon as this issue is closed, we will begin to attract business representatives to use the platform's intellectual resources through the publication of tenders, thus we will begin to attract private investment for the development of new technologies and research.  With the help of crowdfunding system-users will be able to attract funding for the implementation of their ideas from like-minded people or business representatives (who are interested in this technology).  Tender and crowdfunding systems are based on blockchain and use smart contracts, which are backed by our "Science-Token (ST)" based on Ethereum.  Each user will have their own crypto-wallet with our token.  In order to publish a tender - business representatives or just customers - it is necessary to purchase our token on the internal exchange from other token holders and reserve it in a smart contract, after which the tender can be published, and our algorithm for selecting personnel of the necessary qualification will gather the necessary performers for the implementation of the project.  All transactions within our platform are made in our token, however, we plan to work in the international arena and plan to create a holding company legal entities in each jurisdiction that would be people from the traditional financial segment was convenient to use the platform as an intermediary, for the purchase of our token from other users (not all countries allow you to buy cryptocurrency directly from your current account on the exchange , in this case, we will be your agent, as a legal entity. We will conclude contracts and receive investments in the current account of our company in the jurisdiction where crypto purchases from the Bank account are allowed. We will buy the necessary amount of tokens from our users and in the future we will give them to the customer for further use within our system.)  We will also guarantee the legality of the platform and users within the platform - we will have a database of each user and personal data. In case of fraud, the platform will provide the user's contact details and provide legal protection to the injured party on its own.  We plan to become a single international center for communication of the entire scientific and IT community, which would significantly accelerate the introduction of new technologies in everyday life.  We do not pursue the interests of any state, but are fully focused on the development of science.  In the future, as soon as the platform is internationally recognized, as soon as we get licenses and a large number of users-we will start implementing a patent system on the blockchain in the jurisdiction of each country, we will defend the interests of scientists by providing them with legal protection of our platform, under the auspices of the " International Science Hub"  ↗️ ISH Rating: icobench.com/ico/international-science-hub trackico.io/ico/international-science-hub/ icomarks.com/ico/international-science-hub icoholder.com/en/international-science-hub-22242 neironix.io/ru/ico-rating/ish_international_science_hub  🔗 Links: Site: ish.earth WP: ish.earth/wp.pdf Email: ceo@ish.earth Linkedin: linkedin.com/company/ish-earth/ Twitter: twitter.com/ish_earth Telegram ANN: t.me/ish_earth github: github.com/wisdman/science-token reddit: reddit.com/user/ISHearth/

Author: bth1122
Title: 📌⚡[AIRDROP][ANN][ICO][PRESALE] 🌐🔴 ISH - International science hub 🚀 🔴 🌐
Body: ISH 플랫폼 "International Science Hub"는 전문가와 고객 간의 다리를 만들어 과학 발전의 가용성, 품질 및 속도를 높이기위한 분산 형 과학 플랫폼입니다. ISH의 목적은 과학자들을 통합 할 수있는 작업 환경을 조성하는 것입니다. 정보로서의 과학 - 모든 사람이 접근 할 수 있어야합니다. 플랫폼 사용자에게는 가장 복잡하고 시간이 많이 소요되는 프로젝트를 처리하는 데 필요한 모든 기능이 제공되며 기존 프로젝트 관리 솔루션 및 시장과의 긴밀한 통합으로 새로운 도구를 익힐 필요없이 낮은 진입 임계 값을 보장합니다. 전문가들은 잠재력을 실현할 수있는 더 좋은 기회를 갖게됩니다. 그들은 고객을 쉽게 찾고 연구를 수행하고 새로운 과학적 결과를 얻기 위해 필요한 투자를 유치 할 수 있습니다. 전문가는 연구, 개발 또는 회의 참가 결과와 같은 개인 포트폴리오에 자신의 업무를 게시 할 수 있습니다. 고객은 순위 평판 시스템에 의존하여 최단 기간에 모든 수준의 교육 전문가 팀을 구성 할 수 있습니다.
